\section2 For Painted Paths

\list
\li
  \b{Paint Style}
\list
\li
  \c{Filled and Stroked} - the path has independent materials for
  the fill and stroke.
\li
  \c{Filled} - the path has only one material, for the fill.
\li
  \c{Stroked} - the path has only one material, for the stroke.
